headline: Taco Bell and KFC’s Owner Says AI-Driven Marketing Is Boosting Purchases
summary: Yum Brands, the owner of fast-food giants Taco Bell, Pizza Hut and KFC, says new pilots of AI-driven marketing campaigns are increasing purchases and reducing customer churn.
